UID:H7fDgkTb5C8XJH-EH7Mg4
SUMMARY:Seattle Cuba Friendship Committee Informational Picket
DTSTAMP:20260314T153118Z
DTSTART:20260315T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Our comrades with Seattle Cuba Friendship Committee are putting
	 on an informational picket to draw attention to the deepening crisis in C
	uba: \\n“On January 29\\\, President Trump issued an Executive Order decla
	ring a national emergency under the National Emergencies Act\\\, stating t
	hat “the policies\\\, practices\\\, and actions of the Government of Cuba 
	constitute an unusual and extraordinary threat” to U.S. national security 
	and foreign policy. This order intensified the blockade against Cuba to in
	clude a blockade of all oil shipments going to the island.\\nTrump’s goal 
	is to push Cuba to the edge of collapse.\\nIn response\\\, we and other Cu
	ba supporters around the world are mobilizing to protest the cruel and ill
	egal blockade\\\, and encouraging our Congressional representatives to lif
	t it.” \\nJoin our DSA contingent at the rally to stand in solidarity with
	 the Cuban people.\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/seattle-cuba-friendship
	-committee-informational-picket/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/seattle-cuba-friendship-committee-informat
	ional-picket/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
